name: Xu Qi'an
profile: A modern police academy graduate transported to the Dafeng Dynasty. Uses his knowledge of investigation and modern science to solve crimes in an ancient world filled with magic and political intrigue.

name: Princess Lin'an
profile: The second daughter of Emperor Yuanjing. Despite her royal status, she yearns for validation and understanding. Her journey with Xu Qi'an helps her grow from an immature princess to a capable leader.

name: Wei Yuan
profile: The strategic leader of the Guardians and Dafeng's most talented military mind. Once a powerful fighter, he now serves as the mastermind behind the night watch operations, guiding Xu Qi'an through the complex political landscape.

name: Xu Xinnian
profile: Xu Qi'an's cousin and a brilliant student at Yunlu Academy. Sharp-tongued and intelligent, he specializes in military strategy and serves as both ally and intellectual rival to Xu Qi'an.
